'''Duke King''' is the brother of [[Charlotte King]].

==History==
When Big Daddy reached the end of his fight with lung cancer, Charlotte came to Alabama in order to say goodbye. Landry was supposed to turn off the machines, but he was unable to, forcing Charlotte to do it. Duke wouldn't even go into the room.

==Notes and Trivia==
*He wasn't able to enter his father's room while he was dying.
